# Built phase markdown (AI-chat phases)

Files in this folder are **generated** — do not edit by hand. Add a step in **`scripts/build.py`** to emit `content/parts/phases/built/<phase>.md` when you need **static** prompt text for:

`python scripts/generate_prompt.py --phase <phase> --mode static`

Normative background: **abd-skill-builder** library **`process-approach.md`** (in the monorepo’s `abd-skill-builder` skill).
